<lb ed="I" n="0124a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0124a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0124a0101">供養主
