<lb ed="I" n="0124a15" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">及</unclear>合眷等供養佛</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0124b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0124b0101">夫大聖雖遷。遺影須顯。自非
<lb ed="I" n="0124b02" type="honorific"/>建福崇因。刊石記功。河乃流
<lb ed="I" n="0124b03" type="honorific"/>名後代。<note n="0124001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30662"/>＝得【史】</note><app n="0124001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30662"/></rdg></app>勉三塗<note n="0124002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30769"/>＝者【史】</note><app n="0124002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">者</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30769"/></rdg></app>哉。是以
<lb ed="I" n="0124b04" type="honorific"/>都邑主杜照賢。維那杜慧進
<lb ed="I" n="0124b05" type="honorific"/>等十三人。各竭家資。敬造石
<lb ed="I" n="0124b06" type="honorific"/>像一區。上願三寶永隆。國祚
<lb ed="I" n="0124b07" type="honorific"/>康泰。又為師僧父母。因緣眷
<lb ed="I" n="0124b08" type="honorific"/>屬。普及法界眾生。等同正覺。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0125a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　兩側(之一)</cb:mulu><head>之二　兩側(之一)</head>
